N2  - This article presents news briefs related to management scholarship and practice, as of September 1964. The Academy of Management will hold its 24th annual meeting at the Sheraton-Blackstone Hotel in Chicago, Illinois on December 28-30, 1964. The Texas A&M University?s School of Business Administration is offering new M.B.A. degree programs in Accounting, Computer Science, Organization and Administration and Statistics. Edwin B. Flippo is now professor and head of the department of management at the College of Business and Public Administration of the University of Arizona at Tucson.
